title: Eddie Takes The Donut Challenge + Amy Needs Parenting Advice
itunes:title: Eddie Takes The Donut Challenge + Amy Needs Parenting Advice
description:
Eddie has to run two miles, eat a dozen donuts and then run another two more miles all in under an hour for $100 cash. Amy asks for parenting advice after buying her son an incredibly loud toy. Bobby tells the crew what Lunchbox is getting for his surprise.
